{"id":637145,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/【立此存照】2013年之后最严厉的言论控制/","date":"2020-03-02T01:50:00Z","modified":"2020-03-02T01:50:00Z","title":"【立此存照】2013年之后最严厉的言论控制","content":"<p>CDT编者按：3月1日，互联网言论管控新规正式实施。有不少网友认为，这是2013年之后最严厉的言论控制：中共不仅封杀言论；而且同时封杀相关微信号主人；不仅封杀国内而且封杀海外华人；不仅封杀反共言论而且封杀挺共言论（原因是挺中共内的不同派别而不挺习就必须封杀。）并且，中共将网络警察建到县一级，各大网站必须对网警开放。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-637146\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/屏幕快照-2020-03-01-下午8.42.31.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/屏幕快照-2020-03-01-下午8.42.31.png 612w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/屏幕快照-2020-03-01-下午8.42.31-300x232.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-637147\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"865\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-1.jpeg 694w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-1-174x300.jpeg 174w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-1-592x1024.jpeg 592w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-637148\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"880\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2.jpeg 682w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-171x300.jpeg 171w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/2-582x1024.jpeg 582w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-637149\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"872\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-1.jpeg 688w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-1-172x300.jpeg 172w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/3-1-587x1024.jpeg 587w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%AE%A1%E6%8E%A7\">网络管控</a></strong></p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,38921],"tags":[11064,31353,34363,39894,9212]}